{"tid":1478770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[818] 熱門連一個818post都無，你哋忘記晒所有為香港自由而受傷既手足，忘記自己係香港人！！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:24:43.000Z","uid":193823,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"738ed98c01c0ded3fa623d2d077868604f18f583","tid":1478770,"uid":193823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"個個浪費時間討論唔帶乜乜柒柒，又討乜撚論解放軍出動，又福建幫，又黑社會，我地幾百萬人出嚟要驚佢哋，驚佢屠城？！依加已經唔係講呢啲，要士氣要大家出嚟同香港政府講有幾多人係唔接受現在政府既施政，大家出黎最緊要小心、冷靜處理，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認清目標: 黑警，林奠。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n圍機場第二日我哋係做錯，大家士氣大跌，但唔可以放棄，老土啲講句：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有堅持至會成功</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n你話818少你一個唔少，少一個就係少一個，無人可以幫你去，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人可以代你去，有乜重要過香港既未來？？！！</span></span>為左香港既未來，出嚟吧，你問我要帶咩出嚟？？？？仲問！！！<br />\n<br />\n請各位帶埋你身邊既親戚朋友。<br />\n<br />\n自推十次"},{"pid":"674bede0897dc0697a4b915344d99f08ba434a30","tid":1478770,"uid":212217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非係時候要進化喇! 818 同步搞! 後備持久戰plan! </strong><br />\n<br />\n［推上熱門！！！］全港新戰略‐和理非『節奏抗爭』每日9點準時敲擊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475606</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uybaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uybaW.jpg&h=ddfac6a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90357b739f0cf0058d22761d62b07c32c5f2a7b1","tid":1478770,"uid":193823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac445511ebe97f412222cc2e04101467d50a7674","tid":1478770,"uid":193823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"二推"},{"pid":"b2c9e5b6583896592ee6fd3ae853d73e5377857c","tid":1478770,"uid":193823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201